summary:
I am an English teacher willing to give my best to teach my students. I love taking challenges and getting the best of every experience. I am responsible, hardworking, sociable, passionate, perfectionist, dedicated and creative. 
In terms of teaching, I have taught preschool, elementary, high school, and college students, fostering the use of English and getting great results from my students. Besides that, I belong to the national network "teachers of teachers" in both; Spanish and English. I have also taught English teachers in college for a national program in Chile.
My goals are to enjoy my life, grow as a person and professionally, and keep learning languages and teaching-methods to be a better teacher.
